{"id":232476478,"title":"Costco常見的酒，Robert Mondavi Merlot, 好喝 （不專業分享）","content":"我以前唸的母校，學校的音樂廳及劇場就叫Mondavi center，在那邊聽音樂劇還可以出來買一杯 Robert mondavi出產的紅白酒，實在很不錯，但那時不懂欣賞酒，第一次喝還感覺蠻不優的。\n\n但過了N年後，看到Costco有在賣，而且還不便宜就買一罐回家試試，這一試不得了，家裡男女老少都覺得Robert Mondavi的酒好順口哦，香氣也讚。 （對不常喝紅酒的人來說酒體飽滿不優，丹寧太強也不優，這時候酸甜平衡的merlot就對胃口了）\n\n後來也試了同是加州的BV,及Beringer，但就是沒有robert mondavi來的適合自己，以後有機會試試這牌的cabernet，看能不能改變我第一喝不好的印象。\n\n價位：1500上下\n味道：甜味較為突出，尾韻也不錯\n感想：不想喝酸的喝這個就對啦，牌子夠大，雷不多\nhttps://i.imgur.com/OKZI0W3.jpg","excerpt":"我以前唸的母校，學校的音樂廳及劇場就叫Mondavi center，在那邊聽音樂劇還可以出來買一杯 Robert mondavi出產的紅白酒，實在很不錯，但那時不懂欣賞酒，第一次喝還感覺蠻不優的。但過","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"23082c2f-c19d-456c-a805-1e6ac0a36c31","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-10T15:23:06.681Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-10T15:23:06.681Z","commentCount":3,"likeCount":25,"tags":[],"topics":["品酒板","喝酒","葡萄酒","紅酒"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"品酒","forumAlias":"alcohol","school":"加州大學戴維斯分校","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":25}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/OKZI0W3.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"01055780-cff6-4a7f-9424-2e2810929d00","url":"https://i.imgur.com/OKZI0W3l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/OKZI0W3l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/OKZI0W3l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-10T15:23:06.681Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-10T15:23:06.681Z"},{"id":"01055780-cff6-4a7f-9424-2e2810929d00","url":"https://i.imgur.com/OKZI0W3.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/OKZI0W3","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/OKZI0W3l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-10T15:23:06.681Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-10T15:23:06.681Z"}]